headline.main: How to Start a Soccer Chant
headline.print_headline: How to Start a Soccer Chant

lead_paragraph: Park In-bee overcame a 'dirty' double-bogey to leap to the top of the HSBC Women's Champions leaderboard after the Korean fired a second straight five-under-par 67 on Friday to move one clear of the field in a soggy Singapore.
